headline: Hazeltree January Crowdedness Data May Signal Rising Volatility Across Global Hedge Fund Portfolios
summary: NEW YORK & LONDON, February 11, 2026--Global hedge funds experienced volatility in January amid geopolitical headlines, policy shifts, and energy market swings, according to Hazeltree, a leading provider of integrated treasury and liquidity management solutions for alternative asset managers.
